9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Trung-thu-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Quan-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-AEC6I0cqYu-k5cNGd4tJCw">Trung thu dạ Đại Quan viên tức cảnh - 中秋夜大觀園即景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%E1%BA%BF-m%E1%BB%99/poem-H1mLonDD-bFtXrZebFXhSA">Tuế mộ - 歲暮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/V%C3%A3ng-Nam-Ninh/poem-Qv7b3I2-XwrqaKCUV_nCCg">Vãng Nam Ninh - 往南寧</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/V%C4%A9nh-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-tu%E1%BA%A7n-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-03/poem-kXXYMaVj27WnEy6OutGL4Q">Vĩnh Vương đông tuần ca kỳ 03 - 永王東巡歌其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
